        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 3,
      "content": "Sometimes, if a favorite toy breaks, we may feel sad. The Blue Mask tells us that feeling down is okay, and sometimes all you really need is a big hug.",
      "source_page_number": 3,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_003.jpg",
        "filename": "page_003.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
