        "model": "hexgrad/Kokoro-82M"
      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 5,
      "content": "When thunder rolls outside and lights go out at night, fear can creep in. The Purple Mask helps Leo understand that feeling scared of loud noises is a natural reaction.",
      "source_page_number": 5,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_005.jpg",
        "filename": "page_005.jpg",
        "content_type": "image/jpeg"
      },
      "audio": {
