      }
    },
    {
      "page_number": 7,
      "content": "Wow! When something amazing happens, Leo feels a pure delight. He sees that the Orange Mask shows us this wonderful feeling of Surprise, just like finding a secret party.",
      "source_page_number": 7,
      "image": {
        "path": "images/page_007.jpg",
